These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Transport: boat, van
Pet: goat, turtle
1. Pet:goat is in an even position##4
2. Pet:turtle == Transport:van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Transport   | van | boat |
| Pet     | turtle    | goat   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
House: victorian, farmhouse
Pet: turtle, snake
1. Pet:turtle is in an odd position##4
2. House:farmhouse is on the left of House:victorian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| House   | farmhouse | victorian        |
| Pet      | turtle  | snake |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
